<br>
last night in Sol B was one of the funnest groups I have ever been in. I was the ONLY melee.. that's right. We were doing window room. Me at level 34, necro at 33, mage at level 38. That's it. I would pull singles the best I could using Lucids' lullabye, and would use Denon's disruptive discord, Boastful Bellow, and Fufil's Curtailing Chant with switching my drums and horn for the songs max effects, while the mage monster pet pulverized them, necro pet added to damage, necro mes'd any extras, dot'd, and mage nuked the crap while I just sat there playing away, not even meleeing really. It was so much fun, hehe. Bards can do alot of damage with thier songs, and still maintain a low aggro on the hate list. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLPADDING=1 CELLSPACING=0><TR><TD VALIGN=BOTTOM>
